type.name: Imad
type.summary: Represents an Image Space Adapter form.

property.name: BrightnessAdditives
property.summary: Retreives an enumerable collection of Brightness additives.

property.name: BrightnessMultipliers
property.summary: Retreives an enumerable collection of Brightness multipliers.

property.name: ContrastAdditives
property.summary: Retreives an enumerable collection of Contrast additives.

property.name: ContrastMultipliers
property.summary: Retreives an enumerable collection of Contrast multipliers.

property.name: EditorId
property.summary: Gets or sets the Editor ID associated with this form.

property.name: FormId
property.summary: Gets the Form ID associated with this form.

property.name: SaturationAdditives
property.summary: Retreives an enumerable collection of Saturation additives.

property.name: SaturationMultipliers
property.summary: Retreives an enumerable collection of Saturation multipliers.

method.name: HasTag
method.summary: Determines whether this form has been tagged with the specified text.

method.name: Tag
method.summary: Tags this form with the specified text.
